      "date": "2017-02-07 07:04:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHello Quentin,\nI am checking for \"obd->obd_stopping\" in the 2nd patch set to avoid possible corruption. If mdt is cleanup process then the \"lctl set_param mdt.lustre-MDT0000.hsm_control enabled\" will fail with ENOENT.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
