          "tz": 330
        },
        "subject": "LU-9063 hsm: protect cdt_state with mutex lock",
        "message": "LU-9063 hsm: protect cdt_state with mutex lock\n\nThere is a possible race condition between mdt_hsm_cdt_start()\nand mdt_device_fini() which makes cdt_state inconsistent and\nleads to LBUG in hsm_cdt_procfs_fini(). So mdt_hsm_cdt_stop()\nand hsm_cdt_procfs_fini() are protected under cdt_state_lock.\n\nSeagate-bug-id: MRP-3982\nSigned-off-by: vinayakswami hariharmath <vinayakswami.hariharmath@seagate.com>\nChange-Id: Id4c019cbbadff2ebcd72d0f93652d07a29b17c96\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
